# CodePilot AI

CodePilot AI is a Multi-Agent Software Engineering Assistant designed to understand GitHub repositories and help developers with code analysis, documentation, bug detection, and automated software engineering tasks.

## 🚀 Current Progress

### ✅ Milestone 1 - Repository Cloner

Implemented features:

- Clone any public GitHub repository
- FastAPI REST API
- GitPython integration
- Automatic repository management
- Error handling
- Swagger API documentation

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python
- FastAPI
- GitPython
- Pydantic

## Project Roadmap

- [x] Milestone 1 - Repository Cloner
- [ ] Milestone 2 - Repository Parser
- [ ] Milestone 3 - Code Chunking
- [ ] Milestone 4 - Embeddings + Vector Database
- [ ] Milestone 5 - Repository Chat
- [ ] Milestone 6 - Multi-Agent Architecture
- [ ] Milestone 7 - Documentation Agent
- [ ] Milestone 8 - Bug Detection Agent
- [ ] Milestone 9 - Testing Agent
- [ ] Milestone 10 - Frontend Dashboard

## Getting Started

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload
```